WEBVTT

00:02:59.200 --> 00:03:04.136
And I decided right then and there
that I was going to change my attitude

00:03:04.160 --> 00:03:08.800
and I was going to help the world
change its attitude on climate change.

00:03:09.760 --> 00:03:12.736
So I don't know --

00:03:12.760 --> 00:03:14.736
No, just this? Thanks.

00:03:14.760 --> 00:03:15.960
I don't know --

00:03:18.120 --> 00:03:19.656
what you would do

00:03:19.680 --> 00:03:25.120
if you were told
your job is to save the planet.

00:03:25.960 --> 00:03:27.760
Put that on the job description.

00:03:29.040 --> 00:03:31.696
And you have full responsibility,